data.description: This  3 bedroom rowhome in the Bywood section of Upper Darby is right down the street from Michelle Park.  The home features hardwood floors, updated kitchen,  bathroom with separate shower and tub, 3 nice sized bedrooms , an abundance of natural light, off street parking,  a full unfinished basement with laundry area, and more!  Bring your imagination and build a little sweat equity to shine up this diamond and make it your own!   **PLEASE NOTE** that the property is being sold in AS-IS condition, seller will make no repairs. Buyer is responsible for securing the township U&O permit, along with any subsequent repairs mandated by the township or lender. CASH OR CONVENTIONAL buyers only.
